var book = {
	"name": "Ephesians",
	"numChapters": 6,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208A\"></sup>an apostle of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208B\"></sup>Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208C\"></sup>by the will of God,To the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208D\"></sup>saints who are at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208E\"></sup>Ephesus and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208F\"></sup><i>who are</i> faithful in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29208G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29208G\"></sup>Christ Jesus:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29209H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29209H\"></sup>Grace to you and peace from God our Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29210I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29210I\"></sup>Blessed <i>be</i> the God and Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, who has blessed us with every spiritual blessing in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29210J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29210J\"></sup>the heavenly <i>places</i> in Christ,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29211K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29211K\"></sup>He chose us in Him before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29211L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29211L\"></sup>the foundation of the world, that we would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29211M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29211M\"></sup>holy and blameless before Him. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29211N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29211N\"></sup>In love",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29212O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29212O\"></sup>predestined us to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29212P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29212P\"></sup>adoption as sons through Jesus Christ to Himself, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29212Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29212Q\"></sup>according to the kind intention of His will,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29213R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29213R\"></sup>to the praise of the glory of His grace, which He freely bestowed on us in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29213S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29213S\"></sup>the Beloved.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29214T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29214T\"></sup>In Him we have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29214U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29214U\"></sup>redemption <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29214V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29214V\"></sup>through His blood, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29214W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29214W\"></sup>forgiveness of our trespasses, according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29214X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29214X\"></sup>the riches of His grace",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>which He lavished on us. In all wisdom and insight",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29216Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29216Y\"></sup>made known to us the mystery of His will, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29216Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29216Z\"></sup>according to His kind intention which He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29216AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29216AA\"></sup>purposed in Him",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>with a view to an administration suitable to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29217AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29217AB\"></sup>the fullness of the times, <i>that is</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29217AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29217AC\"></sup>the summing up of all things in Christ, things in the heavens and things on the earth. In Him",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>also we <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29218AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29218AD\"></sup>have obtained an inheritance, having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29218AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29218AE\"></sup>predestined <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29218AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29218AF\"></sup>according to His purpose who works all things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29218AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29218AG\"></sup>after the counsel of His will,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>to the end that we who were the first to hope in Christ would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29219AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29219AH\"></sup>to the praise of His glory.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>In Him, you also, after listening to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29220AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29220AI\"></sup>the message of truth, the gospel of your salvation—having also believed, you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29220AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29220AJ\"></sup>sealed in Him with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29220AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29220AK\"></sup>the Holy Spirit of promise,",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29221AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29221AL\"></sup>given as a pledge of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29221AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29221AM\"></sup>our inheritance, with a view to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29221AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29221AN\"></sup>redemption of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29221AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29221AO\"></sup><i>God’s own</i> possession, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29221AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29221AP\"></sup>to the praise of His glory.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>For this reason I too, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29222AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29222AQ\"></sup>having heard of the faith in the Lord Jesus which <i>exists</i> among you and your love for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29222AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29222AR\"></sup>all the saints,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29223AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29223AS\"></sup>do not cease giving thanks for you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29223AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29223AT\"></sup>while making mention <i>of you</i> in my prayers;",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>that the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29224AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29224AU\"></sup>God of our Lord Jesus Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29224AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29224AV\"></sup>the Father of glory, may give to you a spirit of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29224AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29224AW\"></sup>wisdom and of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29224AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29224AX\"></sup>revelation in the knowledge of Him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>I pray that</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29225AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29225AY\"></sup>the eyes of your heart may be enlightened, so that you will know what is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29225AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29225AZ\"></sup>hope of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29225BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29225BA\"></sup>calling, what are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29225BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29225BB\"></sup>the riches of the glory of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29225BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29225BC\"></sup>His inheritance in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29225BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29225BD\"></sup>the saints,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and what is the surpassing greatness of His power toward us who believe. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29226BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29226BE\"></sup><i>These are</i> in accordance with the working of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29226BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29226BF\"></sup>strength of His might",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>which He brought about in Christ, when He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29227BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29227BG\"></sup>raised Him from the dead and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29227BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29227BH\"></sup>seated Him at His right hand in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29227BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29227BI\"></sup>the heavenly <i>places</i>,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>far above <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29228BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29228BJ\"></sup>all rule and authority and power and dominion, and every <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29228BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29228BK\"></sup>name that is named, not only in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29228BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29228BL\"></sup>this age but also in the one to come.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29229BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29229BM\"></sup>put all things in subjection under His feet, and gave Him as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29229BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29229BN\"></sup>head over all things to the church,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>which is His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29230BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29230BO\"></sup>body, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29230BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29230BP\"></sup>fullness of Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29230BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29230BQ\"></sup>fills <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29230BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29230BR\"></sup>all in all."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>And you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29231A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29231A\"></sup>dead in your trespasses and sins,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>in which you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29232B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29232B\"></sup>formerly walked according to the course of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29232C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29232C\"></sup>this world, according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29232D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29232D\"></sup>the prince of the power of the air, of the spirit that is now working in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29232E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29232E\"></sup>the sons of disobedience.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Among them we too all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29233F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29233F\"></sup>formerly lived in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29233G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29233G\"></sup>the lusts of our flesh, indulging the desires of the flesh and of the mind, and were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29233H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29233H\"></sup>by nature <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29233I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29233I\"></sup>children of wrath, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29233J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29233J\"></sup>even as the rest.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But God, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29234K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29234K\"></sup>rich in mercy, because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29234L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29234L\"></sup>His great love with which He loved us,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>even when we were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29235M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29235M\"></sup>dead in our transgressions, made us alive together with Christ (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29235N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29235N\"></sup>by grace you have been saved),",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29236O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29236O\"></sup>raised us up with Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29236P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29236P\"></sup>seated us with Him in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29236Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29236Q\"></sup>the heavenly <i>places</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29236R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29236R\"></sup>Christ Jesus,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so that in the ages to come He might show the surpassing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29237S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29237S\"></sup>riches of His grace in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29237T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29237T\"></sup>kindness toward us in Christ Jesus.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29238U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29238U\"></sup>by grace you have been saved <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29238V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29238V\"></sup>through faith; and that not of yourselves, <i>it is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29238W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29238W\"></sup>the gift of God;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29239X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29239X\"></sup>not as a result of works, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29239Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29239Y\"></sup>no one may boast.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>For we are His workmanship, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29240Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29240Z\"></sup>created in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29240AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29240AA\"></sup>Christ Jesus for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29240AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29240AB\"></sup>good works, which God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29240AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29240AC\"></sup>prepared beforehand so that we would <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29240AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29240AD\"></sup>walk in them.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Therefore remember that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29241AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29241AE\"></sup>formerly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29241AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29241AF\"></sup>you, the Gentiles in the flesh, who are called “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29241AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29241AG\"></sup>Uncircumcision” by the so-called “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29241AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29241AH\"></sup>Circumcision,” <i>which is</i> performed in the flesh by human hands—",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><i>remember</i> that you were at that time separate from Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29242AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29242AI\"></sup>excluded from the commonwealth of Israel, and strangers to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29242AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29242AJ\"></sup>the covenants of promise, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29242AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29242AK\"></sup>no hope and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29242AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29242AL\"></sup>without God in the world.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But now in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29243AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29243AM\"></sup>Christ Jesus you who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29243AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29243AN\"></sup>formerly were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29243AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29243AO\"></sup>far off have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29243AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29243AP\"></sup>been brought near <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29243AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29243AQ\"></sup>by the blood of Christ.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For He Himself is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29244AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29244AR\"></sup>our peace, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29244AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29244AS\"></sup>who made both <i>groups into</i> one and broke down the barrier of the dividing wall,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29245AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29245AT\"></sup>abolishing in His flesh the enmity, <i>which is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29245AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29245AU\"></sup>the Law of commandments <i>contained</i> in ordinances, so that in Himself He might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29245AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29245AV\"></sup>make the two into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29245AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29245AW\"></sup>one new man, <i>thus</i> establishing <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29245AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29245AX\"></sup>peace,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29246AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29246AY\"></sup>reconcile them both in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29246AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29246AZ\"></sup>one body to God through the cross, by it having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29246BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29246BA\"></sup>put to death the enmity.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29247BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29247BB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He came and preached</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29247BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29247BC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">peace to you who were</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29247BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29247BD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">far away, and peace to those who were</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29247BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29247BE\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">near</span>;",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>for through Him we both have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29248BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29248BF\"></sup>our access in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29248BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29248BG\"></sup>one Spirit to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29248BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29248BH\"></sup>the Father.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>So then you are no longer <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29249BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29249BI\"></sup>strangers and aliens, but you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29249BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29249BJ\"></sup>fellow citizens with the saints, and are of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29249BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29249BK\"></sup>God’s household,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29250BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29250BL\"></sup>built on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29250BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29250BM\"></sup>the foundation of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29250BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29250BN\"></sup>the apostles and prophets, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29250BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29250BO\"></sup>Christ Jesus Himself being the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29250BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29250BP\"></sup>corner <i>stone</i>,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29251BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29251BQ\"></sup>in whom the whole building, being fitted together, is growing into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29251BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29251BR\"></sup>a holy temple in the Lord,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>in whom you also are being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29252BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29252BS\"></sup>built together into a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29252BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29252BT\"></sup>dwelling of God in the Spirit."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>For this reason I, Paul, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29253A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29253A\"></sup>the prisoner of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29253B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29253B\"></sup>Christ Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29253C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29253C\"></sup>for the sake of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29253D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29253D\"></sup>Gentiles—",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>if indeed you have heard of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29254E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29254E\"></sup>stewardship of God’s grace which was given to me for you;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29255F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29255F\"></sup>that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29255G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29255G\"></sup>by revelation there was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29255H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29255H\"></sup>made known to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29255I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29255I\"></sup>the mystery, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29255J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29255J\"></sup>as I wrote before in brief.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>By referring to this, when you read you can understand <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29256K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29256K\"></sup>my insight into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29256L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29256L\"></sup>mystery of Christ,",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>which in other generations was not made known to the sons of men, as it has now been revealed to His holy <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29257M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29257M\"></sup>apostles and prophets in the Spirit;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><i>to be specific</i>, that the Gentiles are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29258N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29258N\"></sup>fellow heirs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29258O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29258O\"></sup>fellow members of the body, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29258P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29258P\"></sup>fellow partakers of the promise in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29258Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29258Q\"></sup>Christ Jesus through the gospel,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29259R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29259R\"></sup>of which I was made a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29259S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29259S\"></sup>minister, according to the gift of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29259T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29259T\"></sup>God’s grace which was given to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29259U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29259U\"></sup>according to the working of His power.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>To me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29260V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29260V\"></sup>the very least of all saints, this grace was given, to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29260W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29260W\"></sup>preach to the Gentiles the unfathomable <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29260X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29260X\"></sup>riches of Christ,",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and to bring to light what is the administration of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29261Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29261Y\"></sup>mystery which for ages has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29261Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29261Z\"></sup>hidden in God <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29261AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29261AA\"></sup>who created all things;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>so that the manifold <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29262AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29262AB\"></sup>wisdom of God might now be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29262AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29262AC\"></sup>made known through the church to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29262AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29262AD\"></sup>rulers and the authorities in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29262AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29262AE\"></sup>the heavenly <i>places</i>.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><i>This was</i> in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29263AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29263AF\"></sup>accordance with the eternal purpose which He carried out in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29263AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29263AG\"></sup>Christ Jesus our Lord,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>in whom we have boldness and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29264AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29264AH\"></sup>confident <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29264AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29264AI\"></sup>access through faith in Him.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore I ask you not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29265AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29265AJ\"></sup>to lose heart at my tribulations <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29265AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29265AK\"></sup>on your behalf, for they are your glory.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For this reason I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29266AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29266AL\"></sup>bow my knees before the Father,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>from whom every family in heaven and on earth derives its name,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>that He would grant you, according to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29268AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29268AM\"></sup>the riches of His glory, to be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29268AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29268AN\"></sup>strengthened with power through His Spirit in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29268AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29268AO\"></sup>the inner man,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29269AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29269AP\"></sup>Christ may dwell in your hearts through faith; <i>and</i> that you, being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29269AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29269AQ\"></sup>rooted and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29269AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29269AR\"></sup>grounded in love,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>may be able to comprehend with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29270AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29270AS\"></sup>all the saints what is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29270AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29270AT\"></sup>the breadth and length and height and depth,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and to know <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29271AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29271AU\"></sup>the love of Christ which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29271AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29271AV\"></sup>surpasses knowledge, that you may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29271AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29271AW\"></sup>filled up to all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29271AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29271AX\"></sup>fullness of God.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29272AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29272AY\"></sup>Now to Him who is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29272AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29272AZ\"></sup>able to do far more abundantly beyond all that we ask or think, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29272BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29272BA\"></sup>according to the power that works within us,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29273BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29273BB\"></sup>to Him <i>be</i> the glory in the church and in Christ Jesus to all generations forever and ever. Amen."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Therefore I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29274A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29274A\"></sup>the prisoner of the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29274B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29274B\"></sup>implore you to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29274C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29274C\"></sup>walk in a manner worthy of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29274D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29274D\"></sup>calling with which you have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29274E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29274E\"></sup>called,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29275F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29275F\"></sup>humility and gentleness, with patience, showing tolerance for one another <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29275G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29275G\"></sup>in love,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>being diligent to preserve the unity of the Spirit in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29276H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29276H\"></sup>bond of peace.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><i>There is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29277I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29277I\"></sup>one body and one Spirit, just as also you were called in one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29277J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29277J\"></sup>hope of your calling;",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29278K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29278K\"></sup>one Lord, one faith, one baptism,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>one God and Father of all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29279L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29279L\"></sup>who is over all and through all and in all.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29280M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29280M\"></sup>to each one of us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29280N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29280N\"></sup>grace was given <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29280O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29280O\"></sup>according to the measure of Christ’s gift.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Therefore it says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29281P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29281P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">When He ascended on high</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29281Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29281Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">led captive a host of captives</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And He gave gifts to men</span>.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>(Now this <i>expression</i>, “He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29282R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29282R\"></sup>ascended,” what does it mean except that He also had descended into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29282S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29282S\"></sup>the lower parts of the earth?",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He who descended is Himself also He who ascended <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29283T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29283T\"></sup>far above all the heavens, so that He might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29283U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29283U\"></sup>fill all things.)",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29284V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29284V\"></sup>gave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29284W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29284W\"></sup>some <i>as</i> apostles, and some <i>as</i> prophets, and some <i>as</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29284X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29284X\"></sup>evangelists, and some <i>as</i> pastors and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29284Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29284Y\"></sup>teachers,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29285Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29285Z\"></sup>for the equipping of the saints for the work of service, to the building up of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29285AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29285AA\"></sup>the body of Christ;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>until we all attain to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29286AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29286AB\"></sup>the unity of the faith, and of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29286AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29286AC\"></sup>knowledge of the Son of God, to a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29286AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29286AD\"></sup>mature man, to the measure of the stature which belongs to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29286AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29286AE\"></sup>fullness of Christ.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>As a result, we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29287AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29287AF\"></sup>no longer to be children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29287AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29287AG\"></sup>tossed here and there by waves and carried about by every wind of doctrine, by the trickery of men, by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29287AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29287AH\"></sup>craftiness in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29287AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29287AI\"></sup>deceitful scheming;",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>but speaking the truth <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29288AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29288AJ\"></sup>in love, we are to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29288AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29288AK\"></sup>grow up in all <i>aspects</i> into Him who is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29288AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29288AL\"></sup>head, <i>even</i> Christ,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>from whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29289AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29289AM\"></sup>the whole body, being fitted and held together by what every joint supplies, according to the proper working of each individual part, causes the growth of the body for the building up of itself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29289AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29289AN\"></sup>in love.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29290AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29290AO\"></sup>So this I say, and affirm together with the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29290AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29290AP\"></sup>that you walk no longer just as the Gentiles also walk, in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29290AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29290AQ\"></sup>futility of their mind,",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29291AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29291AR\"></sup>darkened in their understanding, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29291AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29291AS\"></sup>excluded from the life of God because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29291AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29291AT\"></sup>ignorance that is in them, because of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29291AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29291AU\"></sup>hardness of their heart;",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and they, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29292AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29292AV\"></sup>become callous, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29292AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29292AW\"></sup>have given themselves over to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29292AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29292AX\"></sup>sensuality for the practice of every kind of impurity with greediness.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But you did not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29293AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29293AY\"></sup>learn Christ in this way,",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>if indeed you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29294AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29294AZ\"></sup>have heard Him and have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29294BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29294BA\"></sup>been taught in Him, just as truth is in Jesus,",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>that, in reference to your former manner of life, you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29295BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29295BB\"></sup>lay aside the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29295BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29295BC\"></sup>old self, which is being corrupted in accordance with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29295BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29295BD\"></sup>lusts of deceit,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and that you be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29296BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29296BE\"></sup>renewed in the spirit of your mind,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29297BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29297BF\"></sup>put on the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29297BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29297BG\"></sup>new self, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29297BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29297BH\"></sup>in <i>the likeness of</i> God has been created in righteousness and holiness of the truth.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29298BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29298BI\"></sup>laying aside falsehood, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29298BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29298BJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">speak truth each one</span> <i>of you</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">with his neighbor</span>, for we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29298BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29298BK\"></sup>members of one another.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29299BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29299BL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Be angry, and</span> <i>yet</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">do not sin</span>; do not let the sun go down on your anger,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29300BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29300BM\"></sup>give the devil an opportunity.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He who steals must steal no longer; but rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29301BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29301BN\"></sup>he must labor, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29301BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29301BO\"></sup>performing with his own hands what is good, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29301BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29301BP\"></sup>so that he will have <i>something</i> to share with one who has need.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Let no <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29302BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29302BQ\"></sup>unwholesome word proceed from your mouth, but only such <i>a word</i> as is good for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29302BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29302BR\"></sup>edification according to the need <i>of the moment</i>, so that it will give grace to those who hear.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29303BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29303BS\"></sup>Do not grieve the Holy Spirit of God, by whom you were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29303BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29303BT\"></sup>sealed for the day of redemption.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29304BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29304BU\"></sup>Let all bitterness and wrath and anger and clamor and slander be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29304BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29304BV\"></sup>put away from you, along with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29304BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29304BW\"></sup>malice.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29305BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29305BX\"></sup>Be kind to one another, tender-hearted, forgiving each other, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29305BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29305BY\"></sup>just as God in Christ also has forgiven you."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29306A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29306A\"></sup>Therefore be imitators of God, as beloved children;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29307B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29307B\"></sup>walk in love, just as Christ also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29307C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29307C\"></sup>loved you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29307D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29307D\"></sup>gave Himself up for us, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29307E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29307E\"></sup>offering and a sacrifice to God as a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29307F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29307F\"></sup>fragrant aroma.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29308G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29308G\"></sup>immorality or any impurity or greed must not even be named among you, as is proper among saints;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and <i>there must be no</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29309H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29309H\"></sup>filthiness and silly talk, or coarse jesting, which <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29309I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29309I\"></sup>are not fitting, but rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29309J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29309J\"></sup>giving of thanks.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For this you know with certainty, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29310K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29310K\"></sup>no immoral or impure person or covetous man, who is an idolater, has an inheritance in the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29310L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29310L\"></sup>of Christ and God.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29311M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29311M\"></sup>Let no one deceive you with empty words, for because of these things <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29311N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29311N\"></sup>the wrath of God comes upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29311O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29311O\"></sup>the sons of disobedience.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Therefore do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29312P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29312P\"></sup>partakers with them;",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29313Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29313Q\"></sup>you were formerly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29313R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29313R\"></sup>darkness, but now you are Light in the Lord; walk as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29313S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29313S\"></sup>children of Light",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>(for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29314T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29314T\"></sup>the fruit of the Light <i>consists</i> in all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29314U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29314U\"></sup>goodness and righteousness and truth),",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29315V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29315V\"></sup>trying to learn what is pleasing to the Lord.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29316W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29316W\"></sup>Do not participate in the unfruitful <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29316X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29316X\"></sup>deeds of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29316Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29316Y\"></sup>darkness, but instead even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29316Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29316Z\"></sup>expose them;",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>for it is disgraceful even to speak of the things which are done by them in secret.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But all things become visible <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29318AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29318AA\"></sup>when they are exposed by the light, for everything that becomes visible is light.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For this reason it says,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29319AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29319AB\"></sup>Awake, sleeper,And arise from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29319AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29319AC\"></sup>the dead,And Christ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29319AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29319AD\"></sup>will shine on you.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Therefore be careful how you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29320AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29320AE\"></sup>walk, not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29320AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29320AF\"></sup>as unwise men but as wise,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29321AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29321AG\"></sup>making the most of your time, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29321AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29321AH\"></sup>the days are evil.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So then do not be foolish, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29322AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29322AI\"></sup>understand what the will of the Lord is.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29323AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29323AJ\"></sup>do not get drunk with wine, for that is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29323AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29323AK\"></sup>dissipation, but be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29323AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29323AL\"></sup>filled with the Spirit,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29324AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29324AM\"></sup>speaking to one another in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29324AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29324AN\"></sup>psalms and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29324AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29324AO\"></sup>hymns and spiritual <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29324AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29324AP\"></sup>songs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29324AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29324AQ\"></sup>singing and making melody with your heart to the Lord;",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29325AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29325AR\"></sup>always giving thanks for all things in the name of our Lord Jesus Christ to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29325AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29325AS\"></sup>God, even the Father;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29326AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29326AT\"></sup>and be subject to one another in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29326AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29326AU\"></sup>fear of Christ.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29327AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29327AV\"></sup>Wives, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29327AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29327AW\"></sup><i>be subject</i> to your own husbands, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29327AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29327AX\"></sup>as to the Lord.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29328AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29328AY\"></sup>the husband is the head of the wife, as Christ also is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29328AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29328AZ\"></sup>head of the church, He Himself <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29328BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29328BA\"></sup><i>being</i> the Savior of the body.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But as the church is subject to Christ, so also the wives <i>ought to be</i> to their husbands in everything.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29330BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29330BB\"></sup>Husbands, love your wives, just as Christ also loved the church and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29330BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29330BC\"></sup>gave Himself up for her,",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29331BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29331BD\"></sup>so that He might sanctify her, having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29331BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29331BE\"></sup>cleansed her by the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29331BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29331BF\"></sup>washing of water with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29331BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29331BG\"></sup>the word,",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>that He might <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29332BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29332BH\"></sup>present to Himself the church in all her glory, having no spot or wrinkle or any such thing; but that she would be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29332BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29332BI\"></sup>holy and blameless.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So husbands ought also to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29333BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29333BJ\"></sup>love their own wives as their own bodies. He who loves his own wife loves himself;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>for no one ever hated his own flesh, but nourishes and cherishes it, just as Christ also <i>does</i> the church,",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>because we are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29335BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29335BK\"></sup>members of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29335BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29335BL\"></sup>body.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29336BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29336BM\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For this reason a man shall leave his father and mother and shall be joined to his wife, and the two shall become one flesh</span>.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>This mystery is great; but I am speaking with reference to Christ and the church.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>Nevertheless, each individual among you also is to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29338BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29338BN\"></sup>love his own wife even as himself, and the wife must <i>see to it</i> that she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29338BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29338BO\"></sup>respects her husband."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29339A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29339A\"></sup>Children, obey your parents in the Lord, for this is right.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29340B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29340B\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Honor your father and mother</span> (which is the first commandment with a promise),",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">so that it may be well with you, and that you may live long on the earth</span>.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29342C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29342C\"></sup>Fathers, do not provoke your children to anger, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29342D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29342D\"></sup>bring them up in the discipline and instruction of the Lord.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29343E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29343E\"></sup>Slaves, be obedient to those who are your masters according to the flesh, with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29343F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29343F\"></sup>fear and trembling, in the sincerity of your heart, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29343G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29343G\"></sup>as to Christ;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29344H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29344H\"></sup>not by way of eyeservice, as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29344I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29344I\"></sup>men-pleasers, but as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29344J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29344J\"></sup>slaves of Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29344K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29344K\"></sup>doing the will of God from the heart.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>With good will render service, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29345L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29345L\"></sup>as to the Lord, and not to men,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29346M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29346M\"></sup>knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29346N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29346N\"></sup>whatever good thing each one does, this he will receive back from the Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29346O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29346O\"></sup>whether slave or free.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And masters, do the same things to them, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29347P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29347P\"></sup>give up threatening, knowing that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29347Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29347Q\"></sup>both their Master and yours is in heaven, and there is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29347R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29347R\"></sup>no partiality with Him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Finally, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29348S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29348S\"></sup>be strong in the Lord and in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29348T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29348T\"></sup>the strength of His might.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29349U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29349U\"></sup>Put on the full armor of God, so that you will be able to stand firm against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29349V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29349V\"></sup>schemes of the devil.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For our <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350W\"></sup>struggle is not against <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350X\"></sup>flesh and blood, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350Y\"></sup>against the rulers, against the powers, against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350Z\"></sup>world forces of this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350AA\"></sup>darkness, against the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350AB\"></sup>spiritual <i>forces</i> of wickedness in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29350AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29350AC\"></sup>the heavenly <i>places</i>.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore, take up <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29351AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29351AD\"></sup>the full armor of God, so that you will be able to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29351AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29351AE\"></sup>resist in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29351AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29351AF\"></sup>the evil day, and having done everything, to stand firm.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Stand firm therefore, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29352AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29352AG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">having girded your loins with truth</span>, and <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">having</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29352AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29352AH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">put on the breastplate of righteousness</span>,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and having <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29353AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29353AI\"></sup>shod <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">your feet with the preparation of the gospel of peace</span>;",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>in addition to all, taking up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29354AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29354AJ\"></sup>shield of faith with which you will be able to extinguish all the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29354AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29354AK\"></sup>flaming arrows of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29354AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29354AL\"></sup>the evil <i>one</i>.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And take <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29355AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29355AM\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the helmet of salvation</span>, and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29355AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29355AN\"></sup>sword of the Spirit, which is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29355AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29355AO\"></sup>the word of God.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>With all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29356AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29356AP\"></sup>prayer and petition <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29356AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29356AQ\"></sup>pray at all times <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29356AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29356AR\"></sup>in the Spirit, and with this in view, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29356AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29356AS\"></sup>be on the alert with all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29356AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29356AT\"></sup>perseverance and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29356AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29356AU\"></sup>petition for all the saints,",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29357AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29357AV\"></sup><i>pray</i> on my behalf, that utterance may be given to me <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29357AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29357AW\"></sup>in the opening of my mouth, to make known with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29357AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29357AX\"></sup>boldness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29357AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29357AY\"></sup>the mystery of the gospel,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>for which I am an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29358AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29358AZ\"></sup>ambassador <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29358BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29358BA\"></sup>in chains; that in <i>proclaiming</i> it I may speak <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29358BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29358BB\"></sup>boldly, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29358BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29358BC\"></sup>as I ought to speak.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29359BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29359BD\"></sup>But that you also may know about my circumstances, how I am doing, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29359BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29359BE\"></sup>Tychicus, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29359BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29359BF\"></sup>the beloved brother and faithful minister in the Lord, will make everything known to you.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29360BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29360BG\"></sup>I have sent him to you for this very purpose, so that you may know about us, and that he may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29360BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29360BH\"></sup>comfort your hearts.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29361BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29361BI\"></sup>Peace be to the brethren, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-29361BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-29361BJ\"></sup>love with faith, from God the Father and the Lord Jesus Christ.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Grace be with all those who love our Lord Jesus Christ with incorruptible <i>love</i>."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;